    "body" : "The answer below has the real answer, but I thought I&#39;d chime in with one thing I recently learned. If you have collapsed package structures, if you add a new package that has the same root namespace then intellij will be smart enough to expand things out. i.e if i have <code>com.foo.devshorts.model</code> and then i add <code>com.foo.devshorts.controllers</code> it&#39;ll expand out <code>com.foo.devshorts</code>."
